snippet.title: FOX 13 Tampa Bay
snippet.description: The official YouTube home of WTVT-TV, FOX 13 Tampa Bay. Bringing you the important stuff like breaking news, Tampa Bay weather, and local stories. But also plenty of fun stuff, like #WeLiveHere tips, the best of our archives, and all those 'only-in-Florida' stories.
